  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1268909/" class="title-link">本书体现了吕先生史学之功力</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1268909"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1992503/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1992503-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1992503/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">穆好古</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2007-12-28"
      class="main-meta">2007-12-28 02:16:57</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1268909_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  其文颇得乾嘉学者考据之工，其文虽短小，然其中之史学知识却极为丰富，虽其中某些论点为近世考古发现所否定，然其方法颇值得今人学习。

